          before any real-world application. We take no responsibility for errors, hallucinations, or damages 
          arising from AI-generated answers.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">4. Contact us</h2>
        <p>
          Questions about this disclaimer should be directed to:
          <a href="mailto:hi@chirag127.in" class="text-[var(--color-primary)] hover:underline ml-1">hi@chirag127.in</a>
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
